Hello {{tenantName}},

{{landlordName}} has prepared a lease agreement for you to review and sign electronically.

Lease Details:
- Property: {{propertyName}}
- Unit: {{unitIdentifier}}
- Address: {{propertyAddress}}
- Lease Period: {{leaseStartDate}} - {{leaseEndDate}}
- Monthly Rent: ${{monthlyRent}}

Please visit the following link to review and sign your lease:
{{signatureUrl}}

IMPORTANT: This link will expire on {{expiresAt}}. Please review and sign the lease before then.

By signing electronically, you agree that your electronic signature is the legal equivalent of your manual signature.

Best regards,
The {{brandName}} Team
